<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>INTERNATIONAL&#174; VT 365 DIESEL ENGINE - CYLINDER HEAD AND VALVE TRAIN - Component Reassembly -
        High-pressure Oil Rail System
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="5">
        <title>High-pressure Oil Rail System</title>
        <figure id="f2350492" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figd08/D0805.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="no"/>
            <caption>Figure 208. Oil rail assembly</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Align oil rail assembly with oil inlets of each injector.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Tilt oil rail assembly toward engine, align oil rail assembly with case-to-head tube
                assembly, and push down evenly until oil rail assembly is firmly seated.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Hand start bolts M6 x 25 oil rail assembly bolts 1, 2, and 3 until finger tight.</para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f2350492.2" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figd31/D3132.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
                     scalefitheight="232px"/>
            <caption>Figure 209. Torque sequence for oil rail bolts</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Torque bolts to the special torque following the sequence above.</para>
        </step1>
        <specpara>
            <note>
                <para>When installing the hose make sure release ring is in place, before snapping oil hose into oil
                    supply tube.
                </para>
            </note>
        </specpara>
        <figure id="f2350493" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figd08/D0891.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="no"/>
            <caption>Figure 210. Hose to crankcase-to-head tube assembly</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Hose</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Crankcase to head tube assembly</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install hose to crankcase-to-head tube assembly by pushing down firmly until mechanism
                locks. Pull up on hose to make sure it is locked.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f2350494" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figd08/D0892.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="no"/>
            <caption>Figure 211. Hose to oil rail assembly</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Hose</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Oil rail assembly</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install hose to oil rail assembly by pushing down firmly until mechanism locks. Pull up on
                hose to make sure it is locked.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f2350495" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figd09/D0927.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="no"/>
            <caption>Figure 212. Glow plug</caption>
        </figure>
        <para>
            <emph type="bold">Installing Glow Plugs</emph>
        </para>
        <para>Install the glow plugs and tighten to the special torque .</para>
    </svcproc>
